497
00:34:36,074 --> 00:34:38,159
and the downstairs storeroom was opened.

498
00:34:39,577 --> 00:34:41,412
But the safe was empty,

499
00:34:41,496 --> 00:34:44,999
and everything Father Baek loved,
his wine, his chocolate,

500
00:34:46,626 --> 00:34:48,127
and even his cheese were gone!

501
00:34:48,628 --> 00:34:50,129
Seriously!

502
00:34:55,051 --> 00:34:55,968
But…

503
00:34:58,096 --> 00:35:00,681
as I dedicated my youth to this church,

504
00:35:01,599 --> 00:35:02,725
